item.title: The Varied Pedo Destinies of 6 Young Girls
item.description: This is episode 47, and the pedo ring series is drawing to an end (will be 50). This episode can be read alone, but check out 'The Pedo Ring Series Summary Of Episodes' under my author name, englishperv, if you want the fuller picture.

item.title: Nice Bit of Asian Child-Sex
